<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>Headline Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Permissions overhaul: note editing now per-note ownership</li>
      <li>Preset Editor overhaul with Default preset and 18 configurable fields</li>
      <li>Weather temperature constraint system with three-tier fallback</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>New</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>"Set Date & Time" button and "Note Open Mode" setting</li>
      <li>Chronicle content enrichment (@UUID links render)</li>
      <li>Condensing multi-day event bars with hover expand</li>
      <li>Countup/elapsed enricher simple and to parameters</li>
      <li>Custom climate zone template and createClimateZone API</li>
      <li>Dual temperature units (Celsius + Fahrenheit side by side)</li>
      <li>Localized wind directions and cinematic CSS scoping</li>
      <li>Moon anchor "Reset Cycle" for fixed-mode moons</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Improvements</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>"Count as Not Empty" Chronicle content filter</li>
      <li>20+ bug fixes across weather, notes, presets, and UI</li>
      <li>Frameless app close animations</li>
      <li>Localizable ordinal suffixes and date format</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
